snippet.textDisplay:
I just heard about this and I had no idea.
PLEASE DO NOT FORCE US TO SHARE THE ISLAND WITH OTHER ACCOUNTS ON THE SWITCH.
I have a young autistic brother with ADHD, who even though he is on medication, has a hard time controlling himself. He thrives off chaos and negative emotions.
He destroyed my Terraria house and world that I had spent over 600 hours on, then laughed about it.
HE WILL DESTROY MY ISLAND. PLEASE. My mom says he has to be allowed to play it, too, and we can't afford 2 Switches.
PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE DON'T MAKE US SHARE THE ISLAND. At least just let it be an option to share. I will not be able to play this game if I'm forced to play with him. He will destroy everything I work on just to see me cry.
I LOVE ANIMAL CROSSING. I struggle with depression and suicidal thoughts, but knowing this game was coming out a week after my birthday, I decided to try to stick around another year...
I'm serious. I'm alive right now because I wanted to play this game. But now it feels like I will never be able to play it. Please... please let us have our own islands. He'll ruin everything...
snippet.textOriginal:
I just heard about this and I had no idea.
*PLEASE DO NOT FORCE US TO SHARE THE ISLAND WITH OTHER ACCOUNTS ON THE SWITCH.*
I have a young autistic brother with ADHD, who even though he is on medication, has a hard time controlling himself. He thrives off chaos and negative emotions.
He destroyed my Terraria house and world that I had spent over 600 hours on, then laughed about it.
HE WILL DESTROY MY ISLAND. PLEASE. My mom says he has to be allowed to play it, too, and we can't afford 2 Switches.
PLEASE, PLEASE, PLEASE DON'T MAKE US SHARE THE ISLAND. At least just let it be an option to share. I will not be able to play this game if I'm forced to play with him. He will destroy everything I work on just to see me cry.
I LOVE ANIMAL CROSSING. I struggle with depression and suicidal thoughts, but knowing this game was coming out a week after my birthday, I decided to try to stick around another year...
I'm serious. I'm alive right now because I wanted to play this game. But now it feels like I will never be able to play it. Please... please let us have our own islands. He'll ruin everything...
